<template>
  <header class="header-block">
    <LeftItemIcon
      :icon="headerData?.icon"
      :name="headerData?.name"
      @click="selectedGroups()"
    ></LeftItemIcon>
  </header>
</template>
<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue';
import LeftItemIcon from './LeftItem/LeftItemIcon.vue';
import { getGameGroupResp } from '@/views/home/api/protocol';
export default defineComponent({
  props: {
    headerData: {
      type: Object as () => getGameGroupResp,
    },
    gameTotal: {
      type: Number,
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {};
  },

  methods: {
    selectedGroups() {
      // dataCenter.gameConfiguration.currentGameGroup = this.headerData!;
      if (this.headerData) {
        this.$router.push(`/casino/originals?groupId=${this.headerData.id}`);
      }
    },
  },
  components: { LeftItemIcon },
});
</script>

<style lang="less" scoped>
.header-block {
  align-items: center;
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
